This software is in the public domain and
is based on public domain libraries from djbdns and daemontools.


Instalation
===========

1. configure compiler
echo "gcc -O2" > conf-cc
echo "gcc -s" > conf-ld

2. configure directory
echo "/usr/local" > conf-home

3. compile binary
make 

4. install binary
make install

(5). remove target files, objects and static libraries
make clean

Removing
========
make unistall


Debian package
==============
make deb

Solaris Package
===============
make solaris
